Package: chngTrackR
Type: Package
Title: Robust Change Detection in Remote Sensing Imagery
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Rejna", 
           family = "Gauro", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "reznagauro09@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Rejina Gauro <rejina.gauro@stud-mail.uni-wuerzburg.de>
Description: A package to perform raster change detection and track changes over time.
             Implements image differencing workflows for detecting land cover changes 
             in satellite/airborne imagery.Supports radiometric correction, spectral 
             indices (NDVI/NDBI), adaptive thresholding (Otsu, k-means), and 
             validation metrics. Designed for scalability with large rasters using 
             modern spatial packages.
